reviewText: While one reviewer rated this video boring I have to disagree.  A very experienced person in aromatherapy might find it boring, but for someone very new to the subject of aromathery will find this a very good introduction to the art.  It covers a wide range of subjects without overwhealming like a lot of the video's do.  It is a very good place for a someone new to aromatherapy to start!
A woman speaks during the whole video, there are no other image except her face.  It would be better to record it on an audio cassette.
